								 <p>Boost’s cloud service can automatically detect when your site needs the Critical CSS regenerated, and perform this function behind the scenes without requiring you to monitor it manually.</p>'=>'<p>重新產生關鍵 CSS 至關重要，這可讓你在 HTML 或 CSS 架構變更時享有最佳網站速度。 這些事務處理起來可能十分繁複且費時。</p>
								 <p>Boost 的雲端服務可自動偵測你的網站何時需要重新產生關鍵 CSS，不必手動監控就能在背景中執行此功能。</p>','Automatic Critical CSS regeneration'=>'自動重新產生關鍵 CSS','<p>To enhance the speed of your site, with this plan you will need to optimize CSS by using the Manual Critical CSS generation feature whenever you:</p>
								<ul>
									<li>Make theme changes.</li>
									<li>Write a new post/page.</li>
									<li>Edit a post/page.</li>
									<li>Activate, deactivate, or update plugins that impact your site layout or HTML structure.</li>
									<li>Change settings of plugins that impact your site layout or HTML structure.</li>
									<li>Upgrade your WordPress version if the new release includes core CSS changes.</li>
								</ul>'=>'<p>為加快你的網站速度，在使用此方案的情況下，每當你執行下列操作時，就需要使用手動產生關鍵 CSS 功能來最佳化 CSS：</p>
								<ul>
									<li>變更佈景主題。</li>
									<li>撰寫新文章/頁面。</li>
									<li>編輯文章/頁面。</li>
									<li>啟用、停用或更新會影響網站版面配置或 HTML 架構的外掛程式。</li>
									<li>變更會影響網站版面配置或 HTML 架構的外掛程式設定。</li>
									<li>升級包含核心 CSS 變更的 WordPress 新版本。</li>
								</ul>','Manual Critical CSS regeneration'=>'手動重新產生關鍵 CSS','Move important styling information to the start of the page, which helps pages display your content sooner, so your users don’t have to wait for the entire page to load. Commonly referred to as Critical CSS.'=>'將重要樣式資訊移至頁面開頭，這有助於加快頁面顯示內容的速度，讓使用者不必等待系統載入整個頁面。 通常稱為關鍵 CSS。','Source URL: %1$s'=>'來源 URL：%1$s','IP Address: %1$s'=>'IP 位址：%1$s','Time: %1$s'=>'時間：%1$s','nounTrash'=>'回收桶','verbTrash'=>'回收桶','HTTP %d while communicating with WordPress.com'=>'與 WordPress.com 通訊時發生 HTTP %d 錯誤','The url parameter is required'=>'URL 參數為必填','Invalid response from WPCOM API while polling for speed scores'=>'輪詢速度分數時從 WPCOM API 傳回無效回應','Paid Subscribers'=>'付費訂閱者','Ask'=>'詢問','Mark as spam'=>'標記為垃圾訊息','Some themes and plugins have <a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">known conflicts</a> with Jetpack – check the list. (You can also browse the <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jetpack support pages</a> or <a href="%3$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jetpack support forum</a> to see if others have experienced and solved the problem.)'=>'已知 Jetpack 會與某些佈景主題和外掛程式發生<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">衝突</a>，詳情請見清單。 (你也可以瀏覽 <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jetpack 支援網頁</a>或 <a href="%3$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jetpack 支援論壇</a>，查看其他人是否也遭遇相同問題並尋求解決之道。)','We strive to live by the <a href="https://automattic.com/creed/" target="_blank" class="jptracks" data-jptracks-name="jetpack_about_creed" rel="noopener noreferrer">Automattic Creed</a><svg class="gridicons-external" height="24" width="24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><g><path d="M19 13v6c0 1.105-.895 2-2 2H5c-1.105 0-2-.895-2-2V7c0-1.105.895-2 2-2h6v2H5v12h12v-6h2zM13 3v2h4.586l-7.793 7.793 1.414 1.414L19 6.414V11h2V3h-8z"></path></g></svg>'=>'我們堅持實踐 <a href="https://automattic.com/creed/" target="_blank" class="jptracks" data-jptra